<h3>Angle <span style=\"color:red;\">ANG1</span>: %d </h3>\
<h3 style=\"color:blue;\">----------- Sensitive Measurements ----------</h3>\
<h3>Voltage U3: %d </h3>\
<h3>Voltage U4: %d </h3>\
